description: For a few weeks in late spring, thousands of fireflies emerge at the Congaree National Park in South Carolina to blink in synchrony. Scientists are trying to learn their secrets and to protect them.
title: Witnessing the spectacle of synchronous fireflies is ‘like magic’

description: BARK Air says it built its experience "dog first," offering perks like puppucchinos and pheromone blankets. It's flying between New York and LA or London and plans to add more routes soon.
title: Air travel has gone to the dogs — literally. Here’s what to know about BARK Air

description: Aid trucks entered Gaza from southern Israel on Sunday through a new agreement to bypass the Rafah crossing with Egypt after Israeli forces seized the Palestinian side of it earlier this month.
title: Aid trucks begin entering Gaza under agreement with Egypt to bypass Rafah

description: Nicki Minaj's concert in Manchester on Saturday night was postponed after police in Holland discovered marijuana in her bags as she was preparing to leave the country.
title: Nicki Minaj concert postponed after she was detained in Holland over pot

description: The International Organization for Migration on Sunday increased its estimate of the death toll from a massive landslide in Papua New Guinea to more than 670.
title: UN estimates more than 670 killed in Papua New Guinea landslide

description: Donald Trump was booed repeatedly while addressing the Libertarian Party National Convention on Saturday night, with many in the crowd shouting insults.
title: Trump confronts repeated booing during Libertarian convention speech
